name: European Institute of Women's Heallth
tag_list: health, women, policy, disease, europe, cancer, gender--gender-health, news, research
overview:
The European Institute of Women’s Health is an NGO making women’s health and well being a priority for European policy makers at local, regional and international level.

It does this by developing and providing information for women, constantly improving resources and information with research for education and training.

It has specific information projects such as: Cancom, a Cancer Information Project, with news, events, EU statistics,reports.

It has also one of the most comprehensive Engender, gender equity project information sites.

It is currently developing a European health policy web based library. One of the initial subjects in this library will include Gender Health information.

The EIWH is based in Dublin, Ireland.
